Class ActionDispatcher

java.lang.Object
  org.apache.jsieve.samples.james.ActionDispatcher

public class ActionDispatcher
extends java.lang.Object

Singleton Class ActionDispatcher dynamically dispatches an Action depending on the type of Action received at runtime.
